#BLOCK: Pathfinder Savant Special Abilities
Adept Activation			KEY:Pathfinder Savant ~ Adept Activation			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																											DESC:You can always take 10 on Use Magic Device checks, except when activating an item blindly.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.60
Master Scholar			KEY:Pathfinder Savant ~ Master Scholar			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary			DEFINE:PaSSkillBonus|0																					DESC:You add %1 to all Knowledge (arcana), Spellcraft, and Use Magic Device checks. You can always take 10 on Knowledge (arcana) and Spellcraft checks.|PaSSkillBonus																																																																																																																																																																																		BONUS:SKILL|Knowledge (Arcana),Spellcraft,Use Magic Device|PaSSkillBonus																						SOURCEPAGE:p.60
