Esoteric Magic			KEY:Pathfinder Savant ~ Esoteric Magic			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary			DEFINE:PaSEsotericSpells|0																				DESC:You treat %1 spells from any class's spell list as if they were on the spell list of your base spellcasting classes; if your base class could not normally cast that spell, it is treated as 1 level higher.|PaSEsotericSpells																																																																																																																																												BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Esoteric Magic Spell|PaSEsotericSpells																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.60
Glyph Finding			KEY:Pathfinder Savant ~ Glyph Finding			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																											DESC:You can use Spellcraft to find writing-based magical traps (including glyphs, runes, sigils, and symbols) in the same way a rogue can use Perception to search for traps.																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.60
Scroll Master			KEY:Pathfinder Savant ~ Scroll Master			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																											DESC:You use your own caster level instead of the item's caster level when using a scroll or other spell completion item.																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.60
Quick Identification		KEY:Pathfinder Savant ~ Quick Identification		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellLike				DEFINE:PaSIdentifyTimes|0				SPELLS:Pathfinder Savant|TIMES=PaSIdentifyTimes|CASTERLEVEL=PaSLvl|Identify				DESC:You may use identify as a swift action. You may do this %1/day.|PaSIdentifyTimes																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.60
Sigil Master			KEY:Pathfinder Savant ~ Sigil Master			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural			DEFINE:PaSSaveBonus|0																					DESC:You receive a +%1 bonus on saving throws against writing-based magical traps, and if the save is successful you do not trigger the trap. A trap that has already been triggered functions normally against you, though you still receive the saving throw bonus.|PaSSaveBonus																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.60	ASPECT:SaveBonus|+%1 bonus against writing-based magical traps|PaSSaveBonus
Analyze Dweomer			KEY:Pathfinder Savant ~ Analyze Dweomer			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellLike				DEFINE:PaSAnalyzeDuration|0				SPELLS:Pathfinder Savant|TIMES=PaSLvl|TIMEUNIT=rounds/day|CASTERLEVEL=PaSLvl|Analyze Dweomer	DESC:You may use analyze dweomer for %1 rounds/day in 1-round increments.|PaSAnalyzeDuration																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.60
Silence Master			KEY:Pathfinder Savant ~ Silence Master			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																											DESC:You are able to activate spell trigger, spell completion, and command word items silently, substituting a magical gesture for the necessary words. You must be able to make somatic gestures, and know how to activate the item normally. 3/day, you may also cast a spell of 6th level or lower as if using a silent metamagic rod.																																																																		ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Pathfinder Savant ~ Silence Master Metamagic																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.60
Silence Master			KEY:Pathfinder Savant ~ Silence Master Metamagic	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																											DESC:3/day, you may cast a spell of 6th level or lower as if using a silent metamagic rod.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.60	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(As silent metamagic rod, 3/day)	ASPECT:CheckCount|3	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per day
